2.
create Class Person
fields:
    name
    age
    weight

methods:
    eat -> which where we pass as a parameter, how much has one eaten and we increase weight += calories_eaten / 100 accordingly and return new weight
    run -> which where we pass as a parameter, how much burnt and we decrease weight -= calories_burn / 100 accordingly and return new weight

create object of Person in main
print each variable
call each method and print whatever they return
